        "text": "Stacks Considered Harmful? <https://twitter.com/jbclements|@jbclements> &amp; I argue that the conventional presentation of stacks causes misconceptions that are esp problematic for modern programming. Also: Highly unconventional Snap! tooling! Study instruments! Questions interpreters! See:\n<https://blog.brownplt.org/2022/07/07/stacks-dont-stack-up.html>",
